{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":2280,"text":"People returning to work\nafter a career break:"},{"time":5840,"text":"I call them relaunchers."},{"time":8039,"text":"These are people who have taken\ncareer breaks for elder care,"},{"time":11920,"text":"for childcare reasons,"},{"time":13760,"text":"pursuing a personal interest"},{"time":15480,"text":"or a personal health issue."},{"time":18160,"text":"Closely related are\ncareer transitioners of all kinds:"},{"time":21560,"text":"veterans, military spouses,"},{"time":23920,"text":"retirees coming out of retirement"},{"time":26360,"text":"or repatriating expats."},{"time":29760,"text":"Returning to work\nafter a career break is hard"},{"time":32720,"text":"because of a disconnect\nbetween the employers"},{"time":35760,"text":"and the relaunchers."},{"time":37680,"text":"Employers can view hiring people\nwith a gap on their resume"},{"time":41680,"text":"as a high-risk proposition,"},{"time":43800,"text":"and individuals on career break\ncan have doubts about their abilities"},{"time":47680,"text":"to relaunch their careers,"},{"time":49280,"text":"especially if they've been out\nfor a long time."},{"time":52320,"text":"This disconnect is a problem\nthat I'm trying to help solve."}]},{"cues":[{"time":57640,"text":"Now, successful relaunchers\nare everywhere and in every field."},{"time":62680,"text":"This is Sami Kafala."},{"time":64440,"text":"He's a nuclear physicist in the UK"},{"time":67200,"text":"who took a five-year career break\nto be home with his five children."},{"time":72160,"text":"The Singapore press recently wrote\nabout nurses returning to work"},{"time":76120,"text":"after long career breaks."},{"time":78200,"text":"And speaking of long career breaks,"},{"time":80240,"text":"this is Mimi Kahn."},{"time":82120,"text":"She's a social worker\nin Orange County, California,"},{"time":85320,"text":"who returned to work\nin a social services organization"},{"time":88680,"text":"after a 25-year career break."},{"time":91480,"text":"That's the longest career break\nthat I'm aware of."},{"time":94280,"text":"Supreme Court Justice Sandra Day O'Connor"},{"time":96840,"text":"took a five-year career break\nearly in her career."}]},{"cues":[{"time":100720,"text":"And this is Tracy Shapiro,\nwho took a 13-year career break."},{"time":105400,"text":"Tracy answered a call for essays\nby the Today Show"},{"time":109360,"text":"from people who were trying\nto return to work"},{"time":111800,"text":"but having a difficult time of it."},{"time":114160,"text":"Tracy wrote in that she was a mom of five\nwho loved her time at home,"},{"time":118640,"text":"but she had gone through a divorce\nand needed to return to work,"},{"time":122200,"text":"plus she really wanted\nto bring work back into her life"},{"time":125160,"text":"because she loved working."},{"time":127520,"text":"Tracy was doing what so many of us do"},{"time":130120,"text":"when we feel like we've put in\na good day in the job search."},{"time":133880,"text":"She was looking for a finance\nor accounting role,"},{"time":136880,"text":"and she had just spent\nthe last nine months"},{"time":139600,"text":"very diligently researching\ncompanies online"},{"time":142920,"text":"and applying for jobs with no results."}]},{"cues":[{"time":146120,"text":"I met Tracy in June of 2011,"},{"time":149880,"text":"when the Today Show asked me\nif I could work with her"},{"time":153440,"text":"to see if I could help her\nturn things around."},{"time":156160,"text":"The first thing I told Tracy\nwas she had to get out of the house."},{"time":159640,"text":"I told her she had to go public\nwith her job search"},{"time":162400,"text":"and tell everyone she knew\nabout her interest in returning to work."},{"time":166680,"text":"I also told her, \"You are going\nto have a lot of conversations"},{"time":170480,"text":"that don't go anywhere."},{"time":172080,"text":"Expect that, and don't\nbe discouraged by it."},{"time":175360,"text":"There will be a handful"},{"time":176960,"text":"that ultimately lead\nto a job opportunity.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":180680,"text":"I'll tell you what happened\nwith Tracy in a little bit,"},{"time":183320,"text":"but I want to share with you\na discovery that I made"},{"time":185773,"text":"when I was returning to work"},{"time":187520,"text":"after my own career break of 11 years\nout of the full-time workforce."},{"time":191640,"text":"And that is, that people's view of you\nis frozen in time."},{"time":197320,"text":"What I mean by this is,\nwhen you start to get in touch with people"},{"time":201000,"text":"and you get back in touch\nwith those people from the past,"},{"time":203760,"text":"the people with whom you worked\nor went to school,"},{"time":207040,"text":"they are going to remember you as you were"},{"time":209800,"text":"before your career break."},{"time":211640,"text":"And that's even if your sense of self\nhas diminished over time,"},{"time":215160,"text":"as happens with so many of us"},{"time":217280,"text":"the farther removed we are\nfrom our professional identities."},{"time":221200,"text":"So for example,\nyou might think of yourself"},{"time":223920,"text":"as someone who looks like this."},{"time":225800,"text":"This is me, crazy after a day\nof driving around in my minivan."},{"time":230120,"text":"Or here I am in the kitchen."},{"time":232760,"text":"But those people from the past,"},{"time":235320,"text":"they don't know about any of this."},{"time":237560,"text":"They only remember you as you were,"},{"time":240120,"text":"and it's a great confidence boost\nto be back in touch with these people"},{"time":244320,"text":"and hear their enthusiasm\nabout your interest in returning to work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":249440,"text":"There's one more thing I remember vividly\nfrom my own career break."},{"time":253560,"text":"And that was that I hardly kept up\nwith the business news."},{"time":256959,"text":"My background is in finance,"},{"time":258600,"text":"and I hardly kept up with any news"},{"time":261040,"text":"when I was home caring\nfor my four young children."},{"time":264000,"text":"So I was afraid I'd go into an interview"},{"time":267400,"text":"and start talking about a company\nthat didn't exist anymore."},{"time":271200,"text":"So I had to resubscribe\nto the Wall Street Journal"},{"time":274760,"text":"and read it for a good six months\ncover to cover before I felt"},{"time":278240,"text":"like I had a handle on what was going on\nin the business world again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":283880,"text":"I believe relaunchers\nare a gem of the workforce,"},{"time":287560,"text":"and here's why."},{"time":289320,"text":"Think about our life stage:"},{"time":291160,"text":"for those of us who took career breaks\nfor childcare reasons,"},{"time":294840,"text":"we have fewer or no maternity leaves."},{"time":296840,"text":"We did that already."},{"time":298360,"text":"We have fewer spousal\nor partner job relocations."},{"time":301720,"text":"We're in a more settled time of life."},{"time":304200,"text":"We have great work experience."},{"time":306040,"text":"We have a more mature perspective."},{"time":308080,"text":"We're not trying to find ourselves\nat an employer's expense."},{"time":311680,"text":"Plus we have an energy,\nan enthusiasm about returning to work"},{"time":315920,"text":"precisely because we've been\naway from it for a while."}]},{"cues":[{"time":319600,"text":"On the flip side, I speak with employers,"},{"time":322240,"text":"and here are two concerns\nthat employers have"},{"time":324800,"text":"about hiring relaunchers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":326720,"text":"The first one is, employers\nare worried that relaunchers"},{"time":329800,"text":"are technologically obsolete."},{"time":332400,"text":"Now, I can tell you,"},{"time":333680,"text":"having been technologically\nobsolete myself at one point,"},{"time":337280,"text":"that it's a temporary condition."},{"time":339520,"text":"I had done my financial analysis\nso long ago that I used Lotus 1-2-3."},{"time":345680,"text":"I don't know if anyone\ncan even remember back that far,"},{"time":348640,"text":"but I had to relearn it on Excel."},{"time":350880,"text":"It actually wasn't that hard.\nA lot of the commands are the same."},{"time":354600,"text":"I found PowerPoint much more challenging,"},{"time":356840,"text":"but now I use PowerPoint all the time."},{"time":359960,"text":"I tell relaunchers that employers\nexpect them to come to the table"},{"time":364640,"text":"with a working knowledge\nof basic office management software."},{"time":368160,"text":"And if they're not up to speed,"},{"time":369920,"text":"then it's their\nresponsibility to get there."},{"time":372320,"text":"And they do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":373960,"text":"The second area of concern\nthat employers have about relaunchers"},{"time":377600,"text":"is they're worried that relaunchers\ndon't know what they want to do."},{"time":381440,"text":"I tell relaunchers that they need\nto do the hard work"},{"time":384680,"text":"to figure out whether their interests\nand skills have changed"},{"time":388200,"text":"or have not changed"},{"time":389800,"text":"while they have been on career break."},{"time":391640,"text":"That's not the employer's job."},{"time":393920,"text":"It's the relauncher's responsibility\nto demonstrate to the employer"},{"time":398520,"text":"where they can add the most value."}]},{"cues":[{"time":402560,"text":"Back in 2010 I started noticing something."},{"time":406400,"text":"I had been tracking\nreturn to work programs since 2008,"},{"time":410560,"text":"and in 2010, I started noticing"},{"time":413880,"text":"the use of a short-term\npaid work opportunity,"},{"time":417800,"text":"whether it was called\nan internship or not,"},{"time":420280,"text":"but an internship-like experience,"},{"time":422640,"text":"as a way for professionals\nto return to work."},{"time":425800,"text":"I saw Goldman Sachs and Sara Lee"},{"time":428600,"text":"start corporate reentry\ninternship programs."},{"time":431920,"text":"I saw a returning engineer,\na nontraditional reentry candidate,"},{"time":437120,"text":"apply for an entry-level\ninternship program in the military,"},{"time":440960,"text":"and then get a permanent job afterward."},{"time":443880,"text":"I saw two universities\nintegrate internships"},{"time":447600,"text":"into mid-career executive\neducation programs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":451200,"text":"So I wrote a report\nabout what I was seeing,"},{"time":454040,"text":"and it became this article\nfor Harvard Business Review"},{"time":457040,"text":"called \"The 40-Year-Old Intern.\""},{"time":458960,"text":"I have to thank the editors\nthere for that title,"},{"time":461600,"text":"and also for this artwork"},{"time":463000,"text":"where you can see the 40-year-old intern\nin the midst of all the college interns."},{"time":467360,"text":"And then, courtesy of Fox Business News,"},{"time":470560,"text":"they called the concept\n\"The 50-Year-Old Intern.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":473760,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":477600,"text":"So five of the biggest\nfinancial services companies"},{"time":481480,"text":"have reentry internship programs\nfor returning finance professionals."},{"time":485640,"text":"And at this point,\nhundreds of people have participated."},{"time":488960,"text":"These internships are paid,"},{"time":490760,"text":"and the people who move on\nto permanent roles"},{"time":493520,"text":"are commanding competitive salaries."},{"time":496680,"text":"And now, seven of the biggest\nengineering companies"},{"time":500160,"text":"are piloting reentry internship programs\nfor returning engineers"},{"time":504480,"text":"as part of an initiative\nwith the Society of Women Engineers."},{"time":509560,"text":"Now, why are companies embracing\nthe reentry internship?"},{"time":514440,"text":"Because the internship allows the employer"},{"time":517440,"text":"to base their hiring decision\non an actual work sample"},{"time":521480,"text":"instead of a series of interviews,"},{"time":523559,"text":"and the employer does not have to make\nthat permanent hiring decision"},{"time":527320,"text":"until the internship period is over."},{"time":530640,"text":"This testing out period\nremoves the perceived risk"},{"time":534560,"text":"that some managers attach\nto hiring relaunchers,"},{"time":538160,"text":"and they are attracting\nexcellent candidates"},{"time":540840,"text":"who are turning into great hires."}]},{"cues":[{"time":543240,"text":"Think about how far we have come."},{"time":545560,"text":"Before this, most employers\nwere not interested"},{"time":548560,"text":"in engaging with relaunchers at all."},{"time":550920,"text":"But now, not only\nare programs being developed"},{"time":554440,"text":"specifically with relaunchers in mind,"},{"time":557000,"text":"but you can't even apply\nfor these programs"},{"time":559520,"text":"unless you have a gap on your résumé."}]},{"cues":[{"time":562840,"text":"This is the mark of real change,"},{"time":564960,"text":"of true institutional shift,"},{"time":567240,"text":"because if we can solve\nthis problem for relaunchers,"},{"time":570800,"text":"we can solve it for other\ncareer transitioners too."},{"time":574120,"text":"In fact, an employer just told me"},{"time":576080,"text":"that their veterans return to work program"},{"time":578600,"text":"is based on their reentry\ninternship program."},{"time":582000,"text":"And there's no reason why there can't be\na retiree internship program."},{"time":587040,"text":"Different pool, same concept."}]},{"cues":[{"time":590400,"text":"So let me tell you\nwhat happened with Tracy Shapiro."},{"time":592880,"text":"Remember that she had to tell\neveryone she knew"},{"time":595480,"text":"about her interest in returning to work."},{"time":597800,"text":"Well, one critical conversation\nwith another parent in her community"},{"time":602000,"text":"led to a job offer for Tracy,"},{"time":604120,"text":"and it was an accounting job\nin a finance department."},{"time":606920,"text":"But it was a temp job."},{"time":608800,"text":"The company told her\nthere was a possibility"},{"time":611280,"text":"it could turn into something more,\nbut no guarantees."},{"time":614840,"text":"This was in the fall of 2011."},{"time":617720,"text":"Tracy loved this company,\nand she loved the people"},{"time":620760,"text":"and the office was less\nthan 10 minutes from her house."},{"time":623840,"text":"So even though she had a second job offer"},{"time":626080,"text":"at another company\nfor a permanent full-time role,"},{"time":629000,"text":"she decided to take her chances\nwith this internship"},{"time":632240,"text":"and hope for the best."},{"time":635320,"text":"Well, she ended up blowing away\nall of their expectations,"},{"time":638400,"text":"and the company not only\nmade her a permanent offer"},{"time":640920,"text":"at the beginning of 2012,"},{"time":643040,"text":"but they made it even more\ninteresting and challenging,"},{"time":645680,"text":"because they knew what Tracy could handle."}]},{"cues":[{"time":648400,"text":"Fast forward to 2015,"},{"time":650880,"text":"Tracy's been promoted."},{"time":652480,"text":"They've paid for her\nto get her MBA at night."},{"time":654920,"text":"She's even hired another relauncher\nto work for her."},{"time":659840,"text":"Tracy's temp job was a tryout,"},{"time":663240,"text":"just like an internship,"},{"time":664920,"text":"and it ended up being a win\nfor both Tracy and her employer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":671600,"text":"Now, my goal is to bring\nthe reentry internship concept"},{"time":676000,"text":"to more and more employers."},{"time":678760,"text":"But in the meantime,"},{"time":680600,"text":"if you are returning to work\nafter a career break,"},{"time":683840,"text":"don't hesitate to suggest an internship\nor an internship-like arrangement"},{"time":689880,"text":"to an employer that does not have\na formal reentry internship program."},{"time":695520,"text":"Be their first success story,"},{"time":697840,"text":"and you can be the example\nfor more relaunchers to come."}]},{"cues":[{"time":701920,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":703160,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}